Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:05.81,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:07.06,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:08.65,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here's a get well gift...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:10.45,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.45,0:00:13.40,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you remembered my favorite flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:19.54,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry to call you here so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:22.62,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Won't you sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:25.77,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I read in the paper that the choir group
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}took first place in nationals again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:31.02,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not called the choir group anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the choral group.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:07.97,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You're already in costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:10.10,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:12.90,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.43,0:02:15.23,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I dig his enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:29.91,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Esteemed Western District shoppers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:32.54,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Are you enjoying your \Nshopping experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:36.76,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Holy, he really went out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:37.94,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:38.77,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:41.91,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, Sawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:42.97,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I could run...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:47.53,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a heroine, I'm a heroine, I'm a heroine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:50.69,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, team!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:52.81,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.95,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,From the ordinary to the extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:58.61,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,We've got everything you need!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:01.07,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome the Western Shopping District Heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:03.95,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,The WestStoprangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:19.05,Default,Tit,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 10 \NCrushing and Burning
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:27.26,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to need everyone's full cooperation, even those who are busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.51,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,For what, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:32.41,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to get beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:33.27,Default,Men,0000,0000,0000,,Beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:36.01,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Beaten to a pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:41.29,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,The Germ Squad is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:44.46,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let you lay a \Nfinger on the merchandise!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:49.69,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,The Western Shopping \NDistrict's fruit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the best in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.37,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Its veggies are fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:56.63,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this! Curry Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.24,0:04:02.39,Default,Black,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:10.07,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Behold the Power of Curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.44,0:04:12.34,Default,Black2,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, that hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:14.67,Default,Black,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get you for this, WestStoprangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:15.31,Default,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kitaike-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:18.89,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,We've protected the Western \NShopping District's peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:20.12,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,And its tastiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:21.92,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,To celebrate this victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll hold a 30 minute \Nsale, starting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:26.78,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Say the code word for 10% off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:27.87,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,And the code word is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:30.69,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Western Shopping District Heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:33.62,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,The WestStoprangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.41,Default,Boys,0000,0000,0000,,WestStoprangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:36.41,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Did I hear sale?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:37.45,Default,Wom,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:40.38,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Please read this flyer \Nfor more information.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:41.70,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:42.82,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:43.77,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:45.84,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic job, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.62,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:49.85,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Especially for your first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.52,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,We passed out a lot of flyers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.29,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,But we can do so much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:55.08,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Our tempo and timing were subpar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:57.77,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Your hero mode is intense...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:59.46,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hero mode?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.05,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Kitaike-san's toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:02.23,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,He threw his back out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:04.57,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:08.81,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Who can we get to take his place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:13.22,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Desperate times...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:15.62,Default,Five,0000,0000,0000,,For all your shopping needs,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,visit the Western Shopping District!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:19.96,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Mango Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:23.56,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Curry Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:28.09,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, you pesky WestStoprangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.89,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Bacteria Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:36.14,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up, Green!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.36,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,If you fall now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who will protect the peace \Nof the shopping district?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:41.62,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:43.91,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let myself be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:45.41,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:47.82,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Beta Carotene Shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.51,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, WestStoprangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:56.62,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be back again tomorrow, \Nsomewhere in this shopping district!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.12,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Mark my words!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.63,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,We've protected the Western \NShopping District's peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:06.63,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Sakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:11.38,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Western Shopping District Heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:14.35,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,The WestStoprangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:17.40,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy, can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say I make a perfect villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:24.07,Default,Man3,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to let you down like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.07,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, today was a huge success.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:29.68,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is there any way
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you guys would consider \Nextending our agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:33.15,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:34.67,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:36.72,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We have the White Festival coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:39.12,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you \Npractice every day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:43.67,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,But we've barely done anything to get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.86,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Like, wouldn't it'd be hard for you to write
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your song between shifts?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:50.00,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.86,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,So she needs time to figure the song out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:54.62,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,What do you guys think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:57.55,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to do it, \Nit's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:06:59.60,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I can get that song written in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.80,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Shiho-san's done a lot for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it'd be rude \Nto just brush her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.92,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you've \Nfinished anything
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the festival, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:16.26,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to keep going,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but could we maybe have some \Ntime to think it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:20.29,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:28.46,Default,Book,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Lessons in Composition
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:36.94,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you want to know \Nmore about composition,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you should talk to the vice principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:41.14,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The song on that cassette tape
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was co-written by her and your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.19,0:07:56.26,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will now commence singing—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:56.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Too awkward, Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.84,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mahiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:59.64,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll now sing a song
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}born between Nao and me, \Nand nurtured by our choir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:22.44,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamoto-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.60,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,come to the staff room, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:24.81,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.32,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:28.62,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,We'll discuss it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:29.80,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:32.49,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.45,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:35.59,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's about the WestStoprangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:36.82,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,What about 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:39.70,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I saw some girls from the choral \Ngroup watching the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.41,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Why now, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.01,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We had permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:46.59,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,When she's set on something,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she'll spin things any \Nway that suits her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:50.44,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:08:59.34,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:03.63,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you all come?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:06.69,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,If this is about the choir club,\N concerns us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.61,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,So you're all aware, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:13.09,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,that after school jobs are strictly forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:13.89,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:16.17,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have to remind you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to conduct yourselves as students at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:19.95,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We were totally \Nacting like students!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:24.87,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:28.75,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Everything we did, \Nwe did with your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.94,0:09:35.22,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Um, we'd like your stamp of approval...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:41.36,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was before you explained \Nwhat you'd be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.52,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe that makes a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.05,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,The shopping district's customers liked our act.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:53.65,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be using our pay \Nfor the White Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.07,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I fail to see the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.62,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,You're missing the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:59.14,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let it go only \Nif you quit immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:00.53,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,otherwise—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:00.53,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Vice Principal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:05.12,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think going back on something \Nyou've already approved
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is extremely unprofessional?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.42,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.95,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Our club fully intends to finish its job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:15.01,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,What she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.33,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:25.48,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We sure told her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.31,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wien?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:29.35,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Wien.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:31.68,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We schooled her good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:32.56,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for telling her you won't \Nabandon the WestStoprangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:40.33,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, Wien! It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.26,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:46.53,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it'd be all over if \Nwe were ordered to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:48.31,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Thought we'd give in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:49.92,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:53.93,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Once I got into \Nthe role of Curry Yellow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was pretty fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:58.98,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I forget what you call this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:00.62,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I feel abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.74,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean indebted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.62,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, a very poor man named Ted
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:10.04,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,borrowed his best friend's \Nonly coat, named Deb.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:13.05,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,By clothing his friend Ted with Deb the coat, \Nhe coined the term "in-deb-ted."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:15.90,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,It's a touching tale of priceless friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.00,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.90,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely need to share this with Jan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.61,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I know one about \Nflipping your debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:21.61,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.38,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing with him, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:24.50,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,He takes you seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:26.41,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:36.05,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was thinking something like "ta-ri-ra-rira"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:38.75,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that's not what you sang before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:40.13,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:41.22,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes really,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.26,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so which will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:44.33,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.91,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please, Nao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:52.27,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Is your name read as Naoko or Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:57.27,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Your first name, I mean, \NMadam Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:01.86,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Naoko. Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:05.03,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,But my mother called you Nao, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:13.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Recording, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:15.13,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will now commence singing—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:19.19,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes, she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother and I belonged to \Nthe same club in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:23.97,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,The choir club?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:28.26,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. That's what \Nwe called it back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:35.65,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did you ever visit \Nmy mother in the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:55.48,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:59.48,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother wanted to see me, \Nso I went one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:00.42,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:03.22,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:04.56,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:07.48,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,If you're wondering why I didn't tell you that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she and I were acquaintances,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:12.19,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,it's because I must respect \Nthe rules of this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:12.89,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:16.21,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happened in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you are currently nothing \Nmore than one of my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:24.30,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,I will treat you no better \Nnor worse than any other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:25.40,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:29.42,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:31.00,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to ask you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how my mother went about writing songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:38.65,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,You two wrote that song together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:43.17,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to finish a song of hers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:46.04,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,How should I go about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.39,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:10.85,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nao, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:12.32,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:15.05,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:16.50,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which do you like better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:18.12,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should sing, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:20.44,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:21.47,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.21,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't come naturally to me, \Nlike it does for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:26.49,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:29.68,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're just overthinking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.63,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you enjoy singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.09,0:14:36.35,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Music is about having fun with sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:37.60,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've gotta have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:41.54,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're not enjoying yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:46.67,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it if you think you "have" to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.10,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,That's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:51.54,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,A song is something that flows naturally
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the depths of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:15:00.10,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'd appreciate it if you wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,waste my time with such petty concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:05.96,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:23.21,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:24.70,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:27.52,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get well soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:31.69,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sheet music?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:32.58,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:35.92,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd like to write a song with my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:38.41,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like you and I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:41.81,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe if she's accepted to your school,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and joins the choir club, \Nshe could be with you—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:45.54,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the choral group now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:46.59,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.58,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:52.01,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That song, and the original club,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}were both essentially your creations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.37,0:15:57.77,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:00.00,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:01.89,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, Nao.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:03.77,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm glad I could see you one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:06.28,Default,Nao,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:11.27,Default,Mahi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems I'm not going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:38.43,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:39.35,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:43.48,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Some no-name group's \Nalbum isn't worth a dime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:47.44,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,B-But this is a special edition \Nand it's autographed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:50.06,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we could sell it for our festival fund...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:53.51,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we can't keep doing this \Nafter school job thing forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:57.81,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,This is my biggest treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:00.45,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Konatsu, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:04.23,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,I was in a bad mood the other day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:05.54,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,and I lashed out at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:08.05,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:10.21,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,When I said it was \Nrude to reject Shiho-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:12.63,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,But you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:15.65,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,We'll figure out what to do \Nabout the festival together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:16.81,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,If we quit now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be like the vice principal won.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:22.66,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,We can handle the White \NFestival {\i1}and{\i0} a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.14,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,No sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:25.34,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,That an order?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:27.90,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was more pumping myself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:29.48,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:32.63,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:35.32,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Same. And I'll get the song done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:36.32,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:38.54,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to get the script checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:41.08,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:44.08,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,White Festival, here we come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:45.25,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:47.75,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Getting a lot of energy from Yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6} Iwasaki Cleaning
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:52.46,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.38,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:57.02,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Western Shopping District Heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:59.54,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,The WestStoprangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:02.97,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Join us again at 4:30,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in front of the Japanese sweets shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:05.98,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Until we meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:16.61,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,That's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.23,0:18:19.32,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wien!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:29.25,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Evil will not be tolerated!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:36.22,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wien, just leave it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.84,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,A true hero doesn't have \Nthe choice to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:54.07,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:15.13,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dearest Jan:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:19.89,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been busy lately \Nprotecting the world's peace
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as an inheritor of Gamba Red's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:27.10,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thankfully, I have four \Ntrustworthy friends at my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}There!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:31.28,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and they are warriors imbued \Nwith the same passion for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:36.88,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like everyone, a defender of justice \Nhas his share of rough times,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I refuse to get discouraged!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:46.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:50.16,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,You did not just steal a bag back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:53.08,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,That's a proud symbol of \NYellow's dedication to her fri—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:56.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:04.93,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,A hero never gives up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:09.54,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Because {\i1}we...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...keep the Earth turning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:25.57,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can do it! With beads of \Nsweat gleaming in the light,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:32.08,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we reach for the future in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:37.44,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're scared, but that's \Nwhy we'll never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:43.34,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We don't want to regret \Nanything! Not anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:49.54,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dreams we're chasing \Nwon't be easily destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:53.48,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So we'll take hold of it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:57.57,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That moment where we can truly shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:58.44,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:01.49,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gamgam, it's courage time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:04.32,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gamgam, we'll fulfill our duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:10.46,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our passion is blazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:09.68,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What's wrong with you people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:12.54,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Justice! Valor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:14.29,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:16.81,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Western Shopping District Heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:20.28,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,The WestStoprangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:28.80,Default,Headline,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Great work! Local Superheroes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.80,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dear Jan:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:31.79,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wherever you are, I'm sure \Nyou're working hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}just as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:38.43,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe I'll be able to \Ngive these letters to you someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:43.49,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I'll keep on writing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:33.30,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play someone old.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:35.72,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,No way. I don't do art.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:37.98,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,This was originally Wakana \Nand her mother's song.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:40.73,Default,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 11 \NWaxing and Waning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.98,0:23:39.68,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm everyone's mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:40.73,Default,Sakai,0000,0000,0000,,Almost got it.
